      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>新疆香瓜子葵花子春节促销</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --color-primary: #D92D2A;\n            --color-secondary: #F5C045;\n            --color-light: #F4F4F5;\n        }\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--color-light);\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header, section {\n            padding: 2rem 1rem;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--color-primary);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 3rem 1rem;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n        .content-section {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        .content-section h2, \n        .content-section h3 {\n            color: var(--color-primary);\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n        .content-section p {\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        .price-box {\n            background-color: var(--color-secondary);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .promo-banner {\n            background-color: var(--color-primary);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .coupon-center {\n            background-color: #fff8e1;\n        }\n        .product-specs {\n            background-color: #e8f5e9;\n        }\n        .cart-module {\n            background-color: var(--color-secondary);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .reviews {\n            background-color: #fff3e0;\n        }\n        .product-details {\n            background-color: #fff;\n        }\n        .recommendations {\n            background-color: #f0f4c3;\n        }\n        .innovation-module {\n            background-color: #ede7f6;\n        }\n        .sales-broadcast {\n            background-color: #e3f2fd;\n        }\n        @media (min-width: 768px) {\n            body {\n                max-width: 960px;\n                margin: 0 auto;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>欢庆春节，新疆香瓜子葵花子盛大促销</h1>\n        <p>热情祝福佳节，传递品牌温暖，香香瓜子伴您共度团圆时光。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"content-section price-box\">\n        <h2>现价￥29.9 原价￥49.9 限时6折 券后更低</h2>\n        <p>比平时更划算，让您轻松享受高品质香瓜子。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"content-section promo-banner\">\n        <h3>限时抢购剩余 02:15:32</h3>\n        <p>库存紧张，快快下单抢到手！</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"content-section coupon-center\">\n        <h3>领券中心</h3>\n        <p>领取满减优惠券下单立享折上折，使用方便快捷。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"content-section product-specs\">\n        <h3>产品规格</h3>\n        <p>优选新疆香瓜子，颗粒饱满，富含营养膳食纤维。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"content-section cart-module\">\n        <h3>加入购物车</h3>\n        <p>选择数量，加入购物车畅享春节美味。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"content-section reviews\">\n        <h3>用户评分</h3>\n        <p>好评率高达98%，最新评论赞不绝口。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"content-section product-details\">\n        <h3>商品详情</h3>\n        <p>详细的产品介绍、食用方式及图文展示助您放心选购。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"content-section recommendations\">\n        <h3>相似推荐</h3>\n        <p>更多坚果零食精选，为您准备多种美味选择。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"content-section innovation-module\">\n        <h3>春节福袋抽奖</h3>\n        <p>参与互动，赢取惊喜奖品与独家优惠。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"content-section sales-broadcast\">\n       